    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make misogyny and sexism a hate crime",
        "additional_details": "Sexism is rife in the country and for some reason we treat it as a second class offence compared to homophobia and racism. All these types of discrimination are obviously abhorrent but we do not treat them this way. We need people to understand that sexism is just as damaging as any other form of discrimination but why would people believe that if the law doesn\u2019t even recognise that fact?",
        "background": "Make misogyny and sexism as serious a crime as racism and homophobia in the eyes of the law.",
